The paper deals with the problem of Entity Matching (EM) which is a subfield of Database Systems (cs.DB) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed framework involves message passing across neighborhoods which is a technique commonly used in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Distributed Systems (cs.DS). The scalability aspect of the framework also involves optimization techniques which are commonly used in Machine Learning (cs.LG).
